{"tid":1201324,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾夫拿警告：「千萬別跟C朗吃飯！」","createTime":"2019-06-11T04:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T16:49:51.000Z","uid":28938,"like":291,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"dbd5ba22d9e563ee1c81febf06f1eefecf880206","tid":1201324,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"這是曾和C朗拿度在曼聯共事多年的法國後衞艾夫拿給的忠告和警告。<br />\n<br />\n有一次C朗拿度邀請艾夫拿訓練完到家裏吃飯。艾夫拿去了之後發現桌子上只有沙拉、雞肉和水，&ldquo;連果汁都沒有&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n艾夫拿以為接下來會上一些大肉，但到最後還是什麼都沒有。<br />\n<br />\n剛吃完C朗拿度就起身開始踢球，&ldquo;接着他對我説&lsquo;Patrick ，來練習傳球吧&rsquo;&rdquo;艾夫拿説道。<br />\n<br />\nC朗拿度的舉動確實讓艾夫拿有些驚慌失措，我當時在想，&lsquo;能讓我先吃完嗎？&rsquo;艾夫拿説，他補充當時還餓著肚子。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;&lsquo;不，來進行傳球練習吧&rsquo;於是我們就開始練習傳球，在那之後他説一起去游泳，我當時想好吧&hellip;&hellip;然後我們還泡了按摩浴缸，蒸了桑拿，最後我徹底累壞了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n艾夫拿最後憶述，當他受不了，想偷偷離開C朗大宅時，C朗竟從車庫中放了兩頭袋鼠出來，艾夫拿這下不走了，好奇心驅使他駐足看看發生什麼事。<br />\n<br />\n兩頭袋鼠跟著C朗到後花園，C朗架起了發球器，皮球發向空中再墮下，C朗竟然和兩頭袋鼠在一起彈跳爭頂！<br />\n<br />\n艾夫拿：&lsquo;真的是瘋了！他媽的！C朗夾在兩頭畜生中間，竟然跳得比牠們還高！ &rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFY9DeQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFY9DeQ.png&h=ce451982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後艾夫拿總結道：&lsquo;這或許是王騎無法企及的高度吧，所以那條撚屌對C朗一直有種酸酸的情意結。&rsquo;"},{"pid":"5fa4a04bf466bf4af8d6c57c9665125d6c07c1c7","tid":1201324,"uid":5649,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老味袋鼠都出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑到賴屎水"},{"pid":"ab6279d8d8a33a571e112e54b79722b0f882158f","tid":1201324,"uid":25924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb10ec8c63a9c14b3ab7c20f0db692787906236e","tid":1201324,"uid":94828,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"仲以為係食完會俾佢雞姦"},{"pid":"fae608c2a9ed7e80c1033aa0301261fe0525eea1","tid":1201324,"uid":221419,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"Old news is so"},{"pid":"616c67c5e0b579881f4186bdaf62cd4de9a9dff6","tid":1201324,"uid":38938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:07:19.000Z","msg":"9up daily"},{"pid":"910af74a11bfbb28f9b2d40963020edc65291d49","tid":1201324,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357290fb3bb1c64573246a91135e4aab511c11d1","tid":1201324,"uid":5843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"而家先9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f292cb3fff843abd1a39e31865d58df9c0f0bbe","tid":1201324,"uid":40588,"like":99,"dislike":5,"score":94,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"C朗夾在兩頭畜生中間，竟然跳得比牠們還高<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TG7p0h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TG7p0h.png&h=35749f9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbdb9bd6e89c0e701cddd5987fe8ca1764c65c75","tid":1201324,"uid":192589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:12:57.000Z","msg":"他媽的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5640b3364441417e686f6533aef37688512692ba","tid":1201324,"uid":5264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f292cb3fff843abd1a39e31865d58df9c0f0bbe","tid":1201324,"uid":40588,"like":99,"dislike":5,"score":94,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"C朗夾在兩頭畜生中間，竟然跳得比牠們還高<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TG7p0h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TG7p0h.png&h=35749f9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g